      "content": "A \"Solar Throne\" strongly implies a monarchy rooted in divine sanction or power derived from the sun, a motif seen historically in various ancient and medieval cultures. If Aethelgard was deliberately erased, it suggests a powerful entity that was either politically defeated or whose history was deliberately sanitized by a succeeding power. The ring and letters could point toward a powerful, perhaps heretical, or highly localized dynasty whose influence was too disruptive to contemporary state records.",
